'''Buttons''' can be dropped by H.A.M Guards, thieved from [[H.A.M. Member]]s in the [[H.A.M. Hideout]] behind the [[Lumbridge General Store]], earned from the [[Fishing Trawler]] minigame, dug up at the [[Digsite]], or obtained from [[Ogre Coffins]]. You will need at least 15 [[Thieving]] to be able to thieve female H.A.M. Members and 20 Thieving for male H.A.M. Members. They require level 3 [[Crafting]] to polish, yielding 5 Crafting [[experience]] and results in the message: ''"You rub the buttons on your clothes and they become more shiny."'' This changes them into [[polished buttons]], which are used in [[Animal Magnetism]].

